Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:04.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,即使悲傷流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:09.04,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,最終將化作光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.86,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從未停止追求夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:13.42,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,今でも氣付かないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:18.53,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,この靜かな空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:28.50,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつでも思い出すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:33.34,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,もうどこにももどれない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.13,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,そしてずっと心で醒めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:46.34,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,そっと氣付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:51.41,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつかきっとやさしさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:57.28,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,見えてくるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:01.61,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,What's stopping me? I get stuck again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:07.36,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really OK? It's never OK for me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:11.61,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,What's got into me? I get lost again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:18.65,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really OK? It's never going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:13.42,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍未察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:18.53,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,在這寂靜的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:28.50,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然仍然常常想起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:33.34,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,時光一去不復返
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.13,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,一直深藏於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:46.34,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕的告訴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:51.41,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,這份溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:57.28,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,將映入眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:01.61,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼阻止了我嗎? 我再次停住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:07.36,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的可以? 我從未確定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:11.61,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼鑽進我的心中? 我再次得而復失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:18.65,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的可以? 它永遠不會消失

